OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1779329020
OL,3,CIsraeli minister condemned for
OL,4,Ctaunting Gaza flotilla activists in
OL,5,Cvideo
OL,7,FWorld leaders and diplomats have
OL,8,Fcondemned Israel's security minister,
OL,9,FItamar Ben-Gvir, after a video widely
OL,10,Fshared on social media showed him
OL,11,Ftaunting detained flotilla protesters.
OL,13,FThe pro-Palestinian activists were
OL,14,Faboard a Gaza-bound aid vessel, part
OL,15,Fof the Global Sumud Flotilla, which
OL,16,Fwas intercepted by Israeli naval
OL,17,Fforces.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1779329020
OL,3,CIsraeli minister condemned for
OL,4,Ctaunting Gaza flotilla activists in
OL,5,Cvideo
OL,7,FFootage released on Wednesday by Ben-
OL,8,FGvir shows the security minister
OL,9,Faddressing the detainees as they sit
OL,10,Fsurrounded by security personnel, with
OL,11,Ftheir hands bound.
OL,13,FIsraeli ambassadors in several
OL,14,Fcountries have since been summoned
OL,15,Fover the incident.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1779329020
OL,3,CIsraeli minister condemned for
OL,4,Ctaunting Gaza flotilla activists in
OL,5,Cvideo
OL,7,FUK foreign secretary Yvette Cooper
OL,8,Fsaid she was "truly appalled" by the
OL,9,Fvideo, writing on X: "This violates
OL,10,Fthe most basic standards of respect
OL,11,Fand dignity in the way people should
OL,12,Fbe treated.
OL,14,F"We are in touch with the families of
OL,15,Fa number of British nationals involved
OL,16,Fto provide them with consular support."
OL,18,FShe added that the UK had demanded an
OL,19,Fexplanation from the Israeli
OL,20,Fauthorities.
OL,26,@qD@VOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1779329020
OL,3,CIsraeli minister condemned for
OL,4,Ctaunting Gaza flotilla activists in
OL,5,Cvideo
OL,7,FSome 430 detainees arrived in Israel
OL,8,Fon navy ships after trying to pass the
OL,9,FIsraeli blockade of Gaza. Critics call
OL,10,Fthe blockade collective punishment,
OL,11,Fwhile Israel says it's to prevent
OL,12,FHamas from arming.
OL,14,FAs detainees were made to kneel on the
OL,15,Fground on rows with their heads to the
OL,16,Ffloor, Ben-Gvir is shown waving an
OL,17,FIsraeli flag, saying: "Welcome to
OL,18,FIsrael, we are the landlords."
OL,26,@yD@WOUzD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1779329020
OL,3,CIsraeli minister condemned for
OL,4,Ctaunting Gaza flotilla activists in
OL,5,Cvideo
OL,7,FIn another shot, a handcuffed activist
OL,8,Fshouting "Free Palestine" as Ben-Gvir
OL,9,Fwalks past is pushed and held down on
OL,10,Fthe ground by guards.
OL,12,FThe leader of the far-right Otzma
OL,13,FYehudit (Jewish Power) party says in
OL,14,Fanother video that the activists "came
OL,15,Fhere all full of pride like big
OL,16,Fheroes. Look at them now".
OL,26,@vD@bOUxD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1779329020
OL,3,CIsraeli minister condemned for
OL,4,Ctaunting Gaza flotilla activists in
OL,5,Cvideo
OL,7,FHe added: "I say to Prime Minister
OL,8,FNetanyahu, give them to me for a long,
OL,9,Flong time, give them to us for the
OL,10,Fterrorist prisons, that's what it
OL,11,Fshould look like."
OL,13,FPoliticians and diplomats from Israel
OL,14,Fand across the world have since
OL,15,Fcondemned Ben-Gvir over the footage,
OL,16,Fincluding Italian Prime Minister
OL,17,FGiorgia Meloni, who called the scenes
OL,18,F"unacceptable".
OL,26,@oD@KOUsD@RO]zD@AOUzD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1779329020
OL,3,CIsraeli minister condemned for
OL,4,Ctaunting Gaza flotilla activists in
OL,5,Cvideo
OL,7,F"It is inadmissible that these
OL,8,Fdemonstrators, including many Italian
OL,9,Fcitizens, are subjected to this
OL,10,Ftreatment that violates human
OL,11,Fdignity," she wrote on X.
OL,13,F"The Italian government is immediately
OL,14,Ftaking, at the highest institutional
OL,15,Flevels, all necessary steps to secure
OL,16,Fthe immediate release of the Italian
OL,17,Fcitizens involved."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@IO]uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
