FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1779329020
OL,3,CIsraeli minister condemned for
OL,4,Ctaunting Gaza flotilla activists in
OL,5,Cvideo
OL,7,FFrance's foreign minister, Jean-Noel
OL,8,FBarrot, said he had requested that the
OL,9,FIsraeli ambassador to France be
OL,10,Fsummoned to explain the footage.
OL,12,F"The safety of our compatriots is a
OL,13,Fconstant priority," he wrote.
OL,15,F"Whatever one thinks of this flotilla
OL,16,F` and we have indicated on several
OL,17,Foccasions our disapproval of this
OL,18,Finitiative ` our compatriots who are
OL,19,Fparticipating in it must be treated
OL,20,Fwith respect and released as quickly
OL,21,Fas possible."
OL,26,@oD@cxrtD@AOUuD@SO]wD@AOU}D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1779329020
OL,3,CIsraeli minister condemned for
OL,4,Ctaunting Gaza flotilla activists in
OL,5,Cvideo
OL,7,FIreland's foreign minister, Helen
OL,8,FMcEntee, said she was "appalled and
OL,9,Fshocked" by the footage.
OL,11,FIn a statement, she said participants
OL,12,Fof the flotilla, including Irish
OL,13,Fcitizens, "are not in any way being
OL,14,Ftreated with appropriate dignity or
OL,15,Frespect".
OL,17,FSpain's foreign affairs minister, Jose
OL,18,FManuel Albares, branded the treatment
OL,19,Fof the protesters as "monstrous,
OL,20,Fundignified, and humiliating".
OL,26,@pD@WOUqD@HO]uD@KOUwD@HO]yD@frr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1779329020
OL,3,CIsraeli minister condemned for
OL,4,Ctaunting Gaza flotilla activists in
OL,5,Cvideo
OL,7,F"I demand their immediate release and
OL,8,Fapologies from the government of
OL,9,FIsrael," he added.
OL,11,FThe video also drew rare condemnation
OL,12,Ffrom Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin
OL,13,FNetanyahu, who said the actions of his
OL,14,Fcoalition partner were "not in line
OL,15,Fwith Israel's values".
OL,17,F"Israel has every right to prevent
OL,18,Fprovocative flotillas of Hamas
OL,19,Fterrorist supporters from entering our
OL,20,Fterritorial waters and reaching Gaza,"
OL,21,Fhe said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@AOU|D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1779329020
OL,3,CIsraeli minister condemned for
OL,4,Ctaunting Gaza flotilla activists in
OL,5,Cvideo
OL,7,F"However, the way that Minister Ben
OL,8,FGvir dealt with the flotilla activists
OL,9,Fis not in line with Israel's values
OL,10,Fand norms. I have instructed the
OL,11,Frelevant authorities to deport the
OL,12,Fprovocateurs as soon as possible."
OL,14,FIsrael-based legal advocacy group, the
OL,15,FLegal Centre for Arab Minority Rights
OL,16,Fin Israel, or Adalah, accused
OL,17,Fauthorities of "employing a criminal
OL,18,Fpolicy of abuse and humiliation
OL,19,Fagainst activists".
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@bO]yD@POU{D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1779329020
OL,3,CIsraeli minister condemned for
OL,4,Ctaunting Gaza flotilla activists in
OL,5,Cvideo
OL,7,FAdalah said this followed similar
OL,8,Fpatterns of ill-treatment by Israeli
OL,9,Fauthorities against activists in
OL,10,Fprevious flotilla missions "for which
OL,11,FIsrael faced zero accountability".
OL,13,FEven some within Israel's own
OL,14,Fgovernment condemned the security
OL,15,Fminister, with the country's foreign
OL,16,Faffairs minister, Gideon Sa'ar,
OL,17,Fposting: "You knowingly caused harm to
OL,18,Four State in this disgraceful display
OL,19,F- and not for the first time.
OL,26,@rD@\OUsD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1779329020
OL,3,CIsraeli minister condemned for
OL,4,Ctaunting Gaza flotilla activists in
OL,5,Cvideo
OL,7,F"You have undone tremendous,
OL,8,Fprofessional, and successful efforts
OL,9,Fmade by so many people - from IDF
OL,10,Fsoldiers to Foreign Ministry staff and
OL,11,Fmany others. No, you are not the face
OL,12,Fof Israel."
OL,14,FIn a post on X, Israel's Foreign
OL,15,FMinistry shared a series of photos
OL,16,Fshowing security personnel offering
OL,17,Fbottles of water to activists and
OL,18,Fhaving what appear to be calmer
OL,19,Finteractions with them.
OL,26,@tD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
