OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1779329020
OL,3,CIsraeli minister condemned for
OL,4,Ctaunting Gaza flotilla activists in
OL,5,Cvideo
OL,7,FHamas criticised Ben-Gvir for the
OL,8,F"scenes of abuse and humiliation" of
OL,9,Fthe activists, describing it as an
OL,10,Fexpression of Israel's "moral
OL,11,Fdecadence and sadism".
OL,13,FOn Tuesday, Israeli forces boarded the
OL,14,Flast of the flotilla boats that tried
OL,15,Fto challenge the blockade ` the latest
OL,16,Feffort to highlight the grim
OL,17,Fconditions for nearly two million
OL,18,FPalestinians in Gaza.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@aO]rD@XOUsD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1779329020
OL,3,CIsraeli minister condemned for
OL,4,Ctaunting Gaza flotilla activists in
OL,5,Cvideo
OL,7,FFlotilla organisers claimed Israeli
OL,8,Fsoldiers fired on five boats during
OL,9,Fthe interdictions, causing some damage.
OL,11,FIsrael's Foreign Ministry said that no
OL,12,Flive ammunition was fired and that
OL,13,F"nonlethal means" were aimed at the
OL,14,Fvessels as a warning, but without
OL,15,Ftargeting or injuring protesters.
OL,17,FIsrael has called the flotilla "a PR
OL,18,Fstunt at the service of Hamas" with no
OL,19,Freal intent to deliver aid to Gaza.
OL,20,FThe boats carry a symbolic amount of
OL,21,Faid.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@QO]yD@`OUzD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
