FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31616
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1779329020
OL,3,CIsraeli minister condemned for
OL,4,Ctaunting Gaza flotilla activists in
OL,5,Cvideo
OL,7,FIsrael has maintained a sea blockade
OL,8,Fof Gaza since Hamas took control of
OL,9,Fthe territory in 2007, but
OL,10,Frestrictions were intensified after
OL,11,Fthe Hamas-led attacks in southern
OL,12,FIsrael on October 7, 2023.
OL,14,FEgypt, which has the only border
OL,15,Fcrossing with Gaza not controlled by
OL,16,FIsrael, has also greatly restricted
OL,17,Fmovement in and out.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
